Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.83,0:25:11.61,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(296,132)}火憐DaZe！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.54,0:25:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,月火Da☆Yo！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:12.44,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008,132)}月火DaYo！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.62,0:25:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.44,0:25:14.36,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,176)}我們是Fire Sisters！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.83,0:25:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,轉眼間物語系列第二季也要迎來總數第二十話了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(158,184)}黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,118)}出現了一個好厲害的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,228)}連我也
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1066,228)}拿它沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.34,0:25:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,乾脆一口氣播個四十話算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.30,0:25:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就要追上原作了嗎？
